#histogram to analyze numerical variable
plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))
plt.hist(df['QTY'], bins=30, color='LIGHTBLUE', edgecolor='black')
plt.title('Histogram of Numerical Variable')
plt.xlabel('QTY')
plt.ylabel('Frequency')
plt.show()
